0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36757,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/08\/03\/ibn-mubarak-calamity\/","url_meta":{"origin":40350,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Mubarak on Sins: Calamity to not care about your faults","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Husayn reported: Ibn al-Mubarak, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cAmong the greatest of calamities is that a man knows his own shortcomings, but he does not care about them, nor does he grieve over them.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 867 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064f\u0633\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064e\u0643\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40012,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/12\/strength-sirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":40350,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Seerah: Seek strength in the life of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman al-Qasim reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLet the Muslims be strengthened in their calamities by remembering the misfortunes that befell me.\u201d Source: al-Muwat\u0323t\u0323a' 809 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0650\u0645\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18219,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/19\/allah-console-believers-muslims\/","url_meta":{"origin":40350,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Calamity: Allah honors those who console believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 19, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn Hazm reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo believer consoles his brother at the time of calamity but that Allah, glory be to him, will dress him with noble garments on the Day of Resurrection.\" Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1601 Grade: Hasan (fair) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/40350","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-jso